cellent communication skills (Native Portuguese, Fluent English, some Spanish)<br />- Internet &amp; mobile savvy, good understanding of the smartphone<br />&nbsp; ecosystem, social media, internet<br />- Learning fast in general, and specifically on topics related mobile apps<br />- Clear strategic thinker</p><p>If you wish to apply drop us an e-mail with your resume and motivation at <a href="mailto:deise@resultbrazil.com">deise@resultbrazil.com</a></p>]]></description>
